OL,3,CBath's only Hindu Temple to be
OL,4,Cdemolished to make way for new schools
OL,6,FBath's Hindu community could face a
OL,7,F"painful" period without somewhere
OL,8,Fdedicated to worship as their temple
OL,9,Fis to be demolished by the council.
OL,11,FThe city's Shree Jagannatha Temple
OL,12,Fopened in part of the former Culverhay
OL,13,FSchool in 2021, a temporary location
OL,14,Funtil a permanent temple could be
OL,15,Fbuilt.
OL,17,FNow Bath and North East Somerset
OL,18,FCouncil is planning to demolish the
OL,19,Fschool buildings on the site so that
OL,20,Fthe Department for Education can build
OL,21,Ftwo new schools for Bath.
