OL,3,CBath's only Hindu Temple to be
OL,4,Cdemolished to make way for new schools
OL,6,FPaul Roper, the council's cabinet
OL,7,Fmember for economic and cultural
OL,8,Fsustainable development, said the
OL,9,Fcouncil would engage with the temple
OL,10,Fover the plans.
OL,12,FHe said: "We realise the sensitivities
OL,13,Fof it but the need for educational use
OL,14,Fis a strong one."
OL,16,FMost of the school buildings will be
OL,17,Fdemolished in early 2025 but Mr Roper
OL,18,Fsaid the building containing the Hindu
OL,19,FTemple would be retained until July
OL,20,F2025, to meet their requirements to
OL,21,Fmove at certain times.
