OL,3,CBath's only Hindu Temple to be
OL,4,Cdemolished to make way for new schools
OL,6,FHe said: "We are not just kicking them
OL,7,Fout."
OL,9,FThe council expects that not all of
OL,10,Fthe former school site will be needed
OL,11,Ffor the new schools, and part of it
OL,12,Fcould be used for housing or
OL,13,Falternative community uses.
OL,15,FMr Roper said it was possible the
OL,16,FHindu Temple could move into part of
OL,17,Fthis area, but it was yet to be
OL,18,Fdetermined.
