OL,3,CBath's only Hindu Temple to be
OL,4,Cdemolished to make way for new schools
OL,6,FFounding member Susmita Rajhansha
OL,7,Fsaid: "This is, for us, a home,
OL,8,Fbecause every day we come here,
OL,9,Fsitting together, praying together,
OL,10,Feating together, as a whole community.
OL,11,FThis is our first home."
OL,13,FMeanwhile, Ashish Rajhansha of the
OL,14,FHindu Temple said it would take at
OL,15,Fleast six months to build a temporary
OL,16,Fsite for the temple could move into.
OL,18,FHe warned that the temple may have to
OL,19,Fclose for a period if a new location
OL,20,Fcould not be found in time.
