OL,3,CBath's only Hindu Temple to be
OL,4,Cdemolished to make way for new schools
OL,6,F"It will be very painful for us if we
OL,7,Fdon't find somewhere very quickly. We
OL,8,Falways knew we had to move out at some
OL,9,Fpoint but the amount of time is not
OL,10,Fgood enough," he said.
OL,12,FAs well as being the only Hindu Temple
OL,13,Fin the city of Bath, it is the only
OL,14,Ftemple dedicated to Lord Shree
OL,15,FJagannatha in Europe.
OL,17,FMr Rajhansha said: "People come from
OL,18,Fall around the world to visit the
OL,19,Ftemple."
