OL,6,FLord Jagannatha is celebrated each
OL,7,Fyear in the Rath Yatra ` or Chariot
OL,8,FFestival ` where idols of Lord
OL,9,FJagannatha, his sister Subhadra and
OL,10,Felder brother Balbhadra, are paraded
OL,11,Fthrough the streets on a decorated
OL,12,Fchariot.
